Subject: RE: [T2] stainless steel muffler

> Take a look at the Just Kampers website (www.justkampers.co.uk)
> as they do SS exhausts for both sorts of '78 engines (1600 Type 1
> or 2000 Type 4).
> Shouldn't be any sales tax or import duty problems as you're in the EU.


Just a preemptive note that their 2000cc exhausts will not fit '75-78 U.S.
spec busses unless you use '72-74 heat exchangers. The triangular flanged
heat exchangers that we have in North America on those years are not used on
European spec busses.

